Class ApplicantDAO

java.lang.Object
BTOManagementSystem.Model.DAO.ApplicantDAO
public class ApplicantDAO extends Object
DAO (Data Access Object) class responsible for managing data related to Applicants.

Handles operations such as loading from CSV, retrieving users, updating profile details, and persisting changes back to file.
